## Stack

- Svelte 5
- SvelteKit
- TypeScript
- Tauri v2 - Rust based cross-platform desktop app framework
- TailwindCSS
- Bun - package manager

## Tauri v2

Tauri is a framework for building binaries for all major desktop and mobile platforms. We use it
with Svelte + SvelteKit as frontend and Rust for backend logic.

Always reference the official Tauri documentation for the most up-to-date information:
- Documentation: https://tauri.app/start
- Plugins: https://tauri.app/plugin/#features

Always use Bun as package manager for installing packages, e.g. for installing Tauri plugins:

```sh
bun tauri add <plugin-name>
```
